AAE.caption: tableData
AAE.doc: When you pass lists, Bubble separates them with commas and this is what we use to identify cells, if you want to pass Dates (which have commas inside them: Jul 7, 1967 4:04 am) or Texts with commas, use "find and replace" to replace the commas "," with "$comma" so that your data is not broken during processing, do it this way: Text to find "," | Replace with $comma. Don't worry, we'll return your commas later :)
AAE.name: tableData
